[x] If the alarm is armed, then it should be triggered by the door opening.
[x] If the alarm has been triggered, then it can be disarmed, but not armed.
[x] If the door is open, the alarm's current state can not be altered manually.
[x] If the door is open it can be closed.
[x] If the door is closed it can be opened or locked.
[x] If the door is locked it can be unlocked.
